  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK273">
<l>valiyi ṉilaimaiyāṉ valluruvam peṟṟam</l>
<l>puliyiṉṟōl pōrttumēyn taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The assumed appearance of power, by a man who has no power (to restrain his senses and perform austerity), is like a cow feeding on grass covered with a tiger's skin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
